<L>__{interior editing room night}
<A>__{toby and his editor examine the footage on an avid.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{so whaddya think?}
<C>__{editor}
<D>__{well, i'm not really sure what you're trying to say. it's funny, i suppose. but it seems glib and facile to just make fun of how idiotic these people are.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{i'm not making fun. i'm showing it as it really is.}
<C>__{editor}
<D>__{you're showing how superior you are to your subject.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{no, but i like my subject. i like these people.}
<C>__{editor}
<D>__{no, you don't.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{yes, i do. i love them!}
<A>__{pause.}
<C>__{editor}
<D>__{the camerawork's nice.}
<C>__{toby}
<D>__{thanks. i will tell mike.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{well, it's still just a beginning. i know i can...dig deeper.}
